import React from 'react'
import { Image, Divider, Dropdown, } from 'semantic-ui-react'
import iunnologo from '../Assets/iunnologo'

export default class Header extends React.Component {

    render() {

        return (
            <>
                <center>
                    <Divider hidden/>
                    <Image src={iunnologo} />
                    <Divider hidden/>
                    {/* <Divider hidden/> */}
                    <Dropdown basic icon='align justify' floating   className='icon'>
                        <Dropdown.Menu>
                            <Dropdown.Item text='Cancel Order' />
                            <Dropdown.Item text='Edit Profile' />
                            <Dropdown.Item text='Sign Out' />
                        </Dropdown.Menu>
                    </Dropdown>
                </center>
                

        </>

        )
    }

}
